ccre.util

Interface CList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the element type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    CCollection<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CAbstractList, CArrayList, CLinkedList

    public interface CList<E>
extends CCollection<E>
    A list of elements. Unless otherwise specified, this implements the same interface as java.util.List, except that this works across all CCRE platforms, meaning that FRC robot code can use it.
